title: Bionic Commando Rearmed With Crack
description:
This is the Bionic Commando Rearmed game along with the working crack. 

 Thanks go to saioke for the crack and TheOutlawTom for providing the original game download.

 As the comment says, take the paul.dll file in the game directory and replace it with the one provided in this download without starting the game first.

It should work fine if you dont start the game right after the install.
